HEADWORD: Classify
<hw>Clas"si*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Classified</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Classifying</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L.
<ets>classis</ets> class + <ets>-fy</ets>.]</ety> <def>To distribute
into classes; to arrange according to a system; to arrange in sets
according to some method founded on common properties or
characters.</def></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- To arrange; distribute; rank.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Classis</ent>⟦br⟧
